[Title]
WS2812 LED Clock or Wheel of Fortune or ...

[Summary]
This was designed as a clock, but it is customizable and the number of LEDs can be changed as well as the dimensions.

Update 2018-11-17:
Added a center part to mount the electronics controlling the clock. Software and some instructions for an ESP8266 are available at [GitHub](https://github.com/MuellerA/Led-Clock)

[Tags]
WS2812 LED Clock customizable parametric

[Design Tools]
OpenSCAD
